summaryText: Creative and self-starting Frontend Developer with 3 years experience websites and apps in fast-paced, collaborative environments. Passionate about usability and possess working knowledge of Javascript & CSS Frameworks.
descriptionMetropolis: Frontend developer for professional projects. Technology Stack: Nuxt js, Vue js, Javascript ES6, Typescript, Sass, Node, Express, Mongodb, Bulma, Tailwind, Git.
descriptionEveris: Frontend Developer in the Iberdrola Commercial Web project.  Adaptation of responsive designs. JavaScript functionality. Adaptation for Google Tag Manager. Publication and version control. Web application maintenance. Customer support management
descriptionYowi: Desarrollo web front-end con Nuxt Js, Vue Js, Vuetify, Javascript, Bootstrap 4 (Bootstrap Vue), CSS3, Node JS, Express, MongoDB, Mongoose, npm, Nuxt, Vue Cli, Git y Git flow.
